{"tid":717814,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人細個成日用老翻，大個咗開始識得比錢買正版","createTime":"2018-06-26T10:18:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T10:30:51.000Z","uid":174708,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b1306a2164f7b0b2e776db53fcdd1ef7726e9e8e","tid":717814,"uid":174708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T10:18:37.000Z","msg":"細個唔識尊重版權<br />\n最緊要係零用錢食飯都唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 買唔起正版焗住down老翻<br />\n大個咗開始識得買返正版<br />\n買game上返steam買，聽歌就算唔買碟都買sportify/JOOV membership唔會download<br />\n睇電影一係入戲院一係上netflix<br />\n有冇人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係咁<br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲係咩都買老翻"},{"pid":"6a3c10baed789182026938567c06da4a1f4cd7bc","tid":717814,"uid":16061,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T10:22:14.000Z","msg":"大個識搵錢 緊係慳返搵種慢慢破解嘅時間去買啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3598b1efa397d4568c132adef6af441b2ae51e","tid":717814,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T10:25:21.000Z","msg":"多咗錢嘛<br />\n而家破解成本高<br />\n破解版又冇官方update，要成日下載patch咁煩<br />\n又淨係可以同翻版撚玩"},{"pid":"28dd99aa2f0093cfdeff15c7cb52161acf2752db","tid":717814,"uid":170320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T10:30:51.000Z","msg":"睇戲同聽歌都係免費，打機就無計啦。<br />\n宜家大左返工賺到少少錢，而steam 都不時有減價都可以接受到"}]}